# Go backend — content

- Transport: `internal/app/api/content/` — thin handlers, proto mapping in `mapper.go`
- Business logic: `internal/catalog/service/` — `Service` interface
- Persistence: `internal/catalog/repository/` — concrete postgres only
- English code/logs; wrapped errors with `%w`
